How do you set your pc up?  Well, I usually have the monitor up off the desk about 6 inches with it tilted down somewhat to cut off the glare.  My keyboard is right in front of it with the mouse beside it.  The tower is on the floor to the right a bit so I can extend my legs out when I want to stretch.  I also have a corner desk to give a bit more leg room.<P>--------------------<P>Amadeos<BR>Lv41 Sorcerer<BR>Eternus Madidus<BR>Gawaine
