Old template that I used and pass out to everyone that asks. It lets you always charm an even pet. I did not create this but have forgotten who did. <P>Until level 7 throw everything into ming.<P>Then put everything in your secondary skill (usually mind) until it gets to 8<P>Raise Mind until it gets to 12 (you should be at level 15)<P>Raise secondary to 16<P>Raise Mind to 20 (will be at level 26)<P>Other to 23<P>Mind to 32(will be at level 40)<P>Then do whatever your want, I put two more points in mind personally and then dumping the rest to body.<P>--------------------<P>Stroggos<BR>Sorcerer of 45 Pets<BR>Knight of the Sangreal Knights<BR>Igraine Server
</FONT>
