<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
I am a new sorc, and i am wondering if there is there any reason to spec in mind and body? Othen then the aof root what else is in the body spec that is any better then the normal lines? The dd spell is not much better then the lifetap spell. If you spec in both mind and body you wont be able to get the lvl 45 Mind Flay DD spell that does 210 damage, just the lvl 35 Mind Shriek DD spell that does 164 damage. The lvl 45 Superior Essence Consumption life tap spell that does 141 damage is almost as good as the the lvl 35 DD spell and if you are double specing you will get them at around the same time. I know it takes more power and all, but still is it worth double specing? Then again after you get the lvl 32 charm spell there is nothing better in the mind spec....
</FONT>
